You are imaginative: you have a wild imagination. You are fiery: you have a fiery temper, especially when things do not go your way. And you are contrary: you do not shy away from contradicting others.
You are motivated to seek out experiences that provide a strong feeling of sophistication.
You don't find tradition to be particularly motivating for you: you care more about making your own path than following what others have done. You value achieving success a bit more: you seek out opportunities to improve yourself and demonstrate that you are a capable person.

You are unpretentious.
You are self-doubting: you frequently doubt your ability to achieve your goals. You are unstructured: you do not make a lot of time for organization in your daily life. And you are modest: you are uncomfortable being the center of attention.
You are motivated to seek out experiences that provide a strong feeling of connectedness.
